{"tid":731413,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"滙豐預測未來6大新職位，IT最吃香！","createTime":"2018-07-06T07:09:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-08T05:04:21.000Z","uid":1886,"like":3,"dislike":83,"uniUserReply":81,"replies":[{"pid":"e2b51e569d68c0d0fbf8e1561ff213ebdc331b48","tid":731413,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T07:09:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://startupbeat.hkej.com/?p=60954\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstartupbeat.hkej.com%2F%3Fp%3D60954&d=STRXpl6qNaX2zX%2FDPU61dp4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=d932262b\" target=\"_blank\">http://startupbeat.hkej.com/?p=60954</a><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://startupbeat.hkej.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/0706_P11.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstartupbeat.hkej.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F07%2F0706_P11.jpg&h=cc12a92f&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n世界瞬息萬變，各行各業為免落後形勢均積極轉型；滙豐昨發布全新報告，探討銀行業未來發展，預測業界將出現6個出乎意料新職位，包括混合實境體驗設計師（Mixed Reality Experience Designer）、演算工程技師（Algorithm Mechanic）、對話界面設計師（Conversational Interface Designer）、綜合服務顧問（Universal Service Advisor）、數碼處理工程師（Digital Process Engineer），以及合作夥伴把關人員（Partnership Gateway Enabler）。<br />\n<br />\n報告指出，以上6大未來職位均顯示，一系列互通技能將會興起，但滙豐零售銀行及財富管理業務全球創新與合作總監、電子服務平台亞太區主管鄺禮安（Andrew Connell）認為，人工智能並不會取代人類智慧，反而可把先進科技與人類獨有優勢融合，進一步提升服務水平。<br />\n<br />\n報告將該些人類優勢統稱為「3Cs」，即好奇心（Curiosity）、創意（Creativity）和溝通（Communication），又強調因數碼科技人才持續短缺，終身學習及積極提升員工技能，將變得至關重要。而為配合轉型，滙豐現正招聘逾1000名數碼人才，包括UI（使用者界面）設計師、數碼產品經理、軟件工程師、解決方案架構師、探索測試員及交付經理。"},{"pid":"d84b3d0da0475300327340da65ec9f26336c4387","tid":731413,"uid":85659,"like":173,"dislike":0,"score":173,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T07:10:18.000Z","msg":"炒完又吃香?咩玩法??"},{"pid":"f31c47a11fa8c2d46c58f42cd884e42388c87297","tid":731413,"uid":34189,"like":167,"dislike":0,"score":167,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T07:10:40.000Z","msg":"6大炒先職位，IT最吃香！"},{"pid":"e544158a2abac4c2a85133660177099dfb1d10e9","tid":731413,"uid":2566,"like":90,"dislike":1,"score":89,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T07:11:13.000Z","msg":"但HSBC次次搵IT人黎開刀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a438c9594faeaa97401f21471e11e305d182cb7","tid":731413,"uid":1886,"like":3,"dislike":7,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T07:11:52.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/1880000/1884688/cover_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F1880000%2F1884688%2Fcover_1024.jpg&h=62d6d276&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">高登討論區創辦人王國良(DrJim)近年亦指本港IT大有出路。</span></div><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/1884688/高登「花打」：本地+IT+業有得做！\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fezone.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2F1884688%2F%E9%AB%98%E7%99%BB%E3%80%8C%E8%8A%B1%E6%89%93%E3%80%8D%EF%BC%9A%E6%9C%AC%E5%9C%B0%2BIT%2B%E6%A5%AD%E6%9C%89%E5%BE%97%E5%81%9A%EF%BC%81&d=STRXpl6qNaX2zX%2FDPU61dp4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=cc73303d\" target=\"_blank\">https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/1884688/高登「花打」：本地+IT+業有得做！</a>"},{"pid":"9a296e34df5726c60aaa4f77b03024cb8d64b6c3","tid":731413,"uid":25952,"like":75,"dislike":1,"score":74,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T07:14:16.000Z","msg":"香就係香<br />\n不過係拜神個種香<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"859459567afc82300b5c2d0717d0a0a32203f406","tid":731413,"uid":104218,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T07:15:30.000Z","msg":"瓜老襯個種香"},{"pid":"229bd187e72ba3b423066d1d5a0a3988fde7d631","tid":731413,"uid":113626,"like":12,"dislike":2,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T07:16:40.000Z","msg":"又想水人入行 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"720afbe9ce12ea4b228a07ff3b4816bf0b7a8969","tid":731413,"uid":46933,"like":8,"di